DOTVIM README

First stepps:

	Installation:
		
		git clone https://github.com/D1ng5/dotvim.git ~/.vim

	Simbolic links:

		ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
		ls -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

	install Submodules:
	
		cd ~/.vim
		git submodule init
		git submodule update


	add Submodules for instance pathogen
			cd ~/.vim	
                						                           folder of the submodule
		 git submodule add git://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen.git autoload/pathogen
         git add .

(only for pathogen  
    ln -s autoload/pathogen/autoload/pathogen.vim autoload/pathogen.vim
) 
         git commit -m "install patrhogen.vim in the autoload folder"
         
         git push 
          
